description: Investors and Savvy Renters Take Notice!! PRICED TO SELL! Stop paying top dollar for rent and start investing in your future with this charming bi-level 2 bed, 1.5 bath condo in the heart of South Boston! The main level offers two spacious bedrooms, a full bath, in-unit laundry, and direct access to a large private deck—perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Downstairs, enjoy a full kitchen with breakfast bar, a cozy living area with built-in storage, and direct access to your deeded, fenced-in backyard. Original crown molding, exposed brick, and hardwood floors add timeless character throughout. Nestled just off Thomas Park, you're moments from Southie’s vibrant restaurants, shops, bars, and public transit. The perfect rental alternative awaits!
